{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I did get orders, she said, yes, that she could do it, I did not read the small print.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for 50 years, I read small print, because it said if I did leave the Air Corps, I would be-- I would be ready if they needed me for overseas duty.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before I even got orders to go to a-- to a general hospital, I had orders to go overseas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So wonderful, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was really nothing I could do about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only way that I could get out was to become pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it so happened that the unit-- the 127th Evacuation Unit that I was assigned to formed at my husband's camp, which is once in-- one in a million.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They formed the camp at-- the unit at Camp Bowie, Texas.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How they ever got there, I'll never know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I did get there, and they were getting officers and GIs and other nurses from all over the United States to come there to form the unit, we took an apartment in town, where during the week or somewhere, we could be together.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And well, I just didn't get pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I went overseas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So after, it was like a staging area of a couple months that we all got together, and I just waved goodbye to him with tears in our eyes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was like anything else, embarking on a new experience of what would be going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did have meetings about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not know where we were going until the very last minute, because we did get our equipment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did get warm clothes, winter clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
